m89pZei5izABandar Tun Razak Umno to provide free petrol monthlyPublished on Feb 1, 2017Bandar Tun Razak Umno division will provide free petrol to motorcycle riders on the first day of every month.The inaugural event was held this afternoon at a petrol station in Bandar Tun Razak, Kuala Lumpur which saw BN activists pumping petrol for over a hundred motorcycle riders.This scheme was limited to a budget of RM5,000 and only underbone motorcycles with an engine capacity of not more than 150cc would qualify.
